      "message": "I think that name and ID are going to be inherently confusing, so I\u0027m not sure of a good way to phrase it any /less/ confusingly... Adding the link definitely helps though.\n\nMaybe \"The name of the resource associated with this invocation; see also https://aip.dev/122\"?",
