      "message": "it is unclear what is \"resource associated with this invocation\". The invocation *is* the resource here, so applying this to your sentence is \"The name of this invocation, see also https://aip.dev/122\"? \n\nbut still, it does not solve the problem I intend to solve. I\u0027d like this documentation to explain that this string can be used to refer to this invocation. So how about\n\n  // The name of this invocation, see also https://aip.dev/122\n  // Can be used to refer to this invocation, e.g. in GetInvocation.",
